        <Parent_String>Poaceae (family) [300343828], Poales (order) [300375086], Liliopsida (class) [300375592], Angiospermae (division) [300265706], Plantae (kingdom) [300132360], Eukaryota (domain) [300265677], living organisms (entities) [300390503], Living Organisms (hierarchy name) [300265673], Agents Facet [300264089]</Parent_String>
